1233.name: ER 630 (17-4 PH)
1233.Applications: To be used in the as welded condition or in the heat treated condition to obtain higher strength. Mechanical properties of this alloy are greatly influenced by the heat treatment.
1233.Suitable_For: Suitable for precipitation hardening stainless steel used for welding materials of similar chemical composition such as 17-4 (PH) and 17-7 as aplied for valves, fasteners, gears, propeller stafts, and roller chain pins. W.Nr: 1.4542
